  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Admin cum Drafter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>Established in December 2014, Foodco SG Pte Ltd (FCSG) specialises in the supply and maintenance of refrigeration systems, providing reliable solutions to support our clients’ operational needs.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Support operational efficiency by managing office documentation, financial transactions, and technical drawings to enable seamless project execution and administrative functions.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare, organize, and maintain office documentation including files, reports, and correspondence to ensure accurate record-keeping and accessibility</li><li>Create and issue invoices, delivery orders (DO), and quotations to support timely financial processing and client communications</li><li>Process accounts receivable and payable tasks to assist in maintaining accurate financial records </li><li>Collaborate with the project management team by providing administrative support to facilitate project coordination and execution</li><li>Produce and update CAD drawings or assist engineers and designers to deliver precise technical documentation for projects</li><li>Perform ad-hoc administrative duties as assigned to support overall office operations and project needs</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Proficiency in AutoCAD for producing and updating technical drawings</li><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in an administrative and accounts assistant role</li></ul>",
